class Solution:
    def maximumUniqueSubarray(self, nums: List[int]) -> int:
        sub: deque[int] = deque()
        sub_nums: set[int] = set()
        cur_sum: int = 0
        max_sum: int = 0
        for num in nums:
            while num in sub_nums:
                sub_num = sub.popleft()
                sub_nums.remove(sub_num)
                cur_sum -= sub_num
            sub.append(num)
            sub_nums.add(num)
            cur_sum += num
            max_sum = max(cur_sum, max_sum)
        return max_sum
